# ── Supabase Credentials ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get these from your Supabase project → Project Settings → API
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-key-here

# ── Instructions ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Create a free project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Run the SQL in supabase/schema.sql in → SQL Editor → New Query
# 3. Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values
# 4. On Vercel: add these as Environment Variables in project settings
#
# If Supabase vars are missing, the app runs in DEMO mode (localStorage only).
# AI Food Quality Analysis runs entirely in-browser — no API key needed.
